id":33258,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/08\/19\/two-inevitabilities-of-life\/","url_meta":{"origin":33296,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Tawhid: What are two inevitabilities of life?","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 19, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Jabir reported: A man came to the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, saying, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, what are the two inevitabilities?\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cWhoever dies without associating anything with Allah will enter Paradise, and whoever dies associating anything with Allah will enter Hellfire.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":2016,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/02\/28\/hereafter-faith-eventually-jannah\/","url_meta":{"origin":33296,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Akhirah: Whoever has faith eventually enters Paradise","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"February 28, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Dharr reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cGabriel, upon him be peace, came to me to give the good news that anyone from my nation who dies without associating partners with Allah will eventually enter Paradise.\u201d I said, \u201cEven if he commits adultery\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":11374,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/01\/16\/iman-prophet-relations-jannah\/","url_meta":{"origin":33296,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Faith: Relations with the Prophet do not guarantee Paradise","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 16, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas ibn Malik reported: A man said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, where is my father?\u201d The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cHe is in Hellfire.\u201d When he turned away, the Prophet called to him and he said, \u201cVerily, my father and your father are in Hellfire.\u201d Source:\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":1420,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2011\/11\/11\/99-names-allah-asma-al-husna\/","url_meta":{"origin":33296,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on 99 Names: Whoever acts upon them enters Paradise","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"November 11, 2011","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \"Allah has ninety-nine names. Whoever preserves\u00a0them will enter Paradise.\" Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 7392, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 2677 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi (authenticity agreed upon) according to Al-Bukhari and Muslim \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0647\u064f\u0631\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0631\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0646\u064e\u0651\u0628\u0650\u064a\u0650\u0651 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0645\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0644\u0650\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u0650\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":1068,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2011\/10\/28\/all-jannah-but-refuse\/","url_meta":{"origin":33296,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Sunnah: All Muslims enter Paradise but those who refuse","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 28, 2011","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \"Everyone from my nation will enter Paradise but those who refuse.\" They said, \"O Messenger of Allah, who will refuse?\" The Prophet said, \"Whoever obeys me enters Paradise, and whoever disobeys me has refused.\" Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/33296","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/3712"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=33296"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/33296\/revisions"}],"wp:attach